query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci t chn) NoMergeJoin(chn ci t mc) */ select min(chn.name) AS uncredited_voiced_character,
min(t.title) AS russian_movie
from title AS t
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2003 AND ci.note like '%(voice)%' AND ci.note like '%(uncredited)%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id;
